com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.impl

Interface Versioned

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLockOperation, AwaitBackupOperation, AwaitOperation, BeforeAwaitBackupOperation, BeforeAwaitOperation, CacheEventJournalReadResultSetImpl, ClassData, DeregistrationOperation, FinalizeJoinOp, GetLockCountOperation, GetRemainingLeaseTimeOperation, HeartbeatOp, IsLockedOperation, LocalLockCleanupOperation, LockBackupOperation, LockOperation, LockReplicationOperation, LockStoreImpl, MapEventJournalReadResultSetImpl, MapReplicationStateHolder, MasterConfirmationOp, MembersUpdateOp, PartitionBackupReplicaAntiEntropyOperation, PartitionReplicaSyncRequest, PartitionReplicaSyncResponse, PartitionReplicaSyncRetryResponse, ReadResultSetImpl, RegistrationOperation, ReplicationOperation, RingbufferContainer, SignalBackupOperation, SignalOperation, SplitBrainJoinMessage, UnlockBackupOperation, UnlockIfLeaseExpiredOperation, UnlockOperation

    public interface Versioned
    Marker interface that enables marking a DataSerializable or IdentifiedDataSerializable class for versioning. If the serializer supports versioning it will act accordingly to its implementation.
